reviewText: My 4 year old grandbaby enjoys this vhs. Grandma is very price conscience or cheap so I buy as many in vhs as I can. She loves the Cedarmont kids tapes.

My mother-in-law bought this video for my daughter when she was young.  I was looking for videos the other day for my three year old granddaughter and came across this.  My granddaughter LOVES this video.  She watches it OVER and OVER and OVER.  It is older, dated and corny, but she loves it!  We even find ourselves singing the songs!
My 5 month old loves this video and usually makes it the whole way through...Caution..the songs stick in your head all day..LOL
